# Brute-Force Attacks in Web Applications

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Project-BruteForce-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green)

## ğŸ” Overview

This project demonstrates a brute-force attack simulation on a test website using open-source tools such as Hydra, Crunch, CeWL, and SecLists. It accompanies a research paper written as part of a cybersecurity academic program at Purdue Global University.

